docs.snippet: Here is a transcript of those comments, as prepared by the White House.
docs.lead_paragraph: President Trump spoke to reporters Friday morning at the White House and at Joint Base Andrews on his way to Dallas to speak at the National Rifle Association’s annual convention. He was asked about comments his lawyer, Rudolph W. Giuliani, made about payments to the pornographic actress Stephanie Clifford, who goes by the stage name Stormy Daniels. Mr. Trump said Mr. Giuliani did not have his “facts straight,” and that everything about the payments “has been said incorrectly.” Mr. Trump also said a date and location had been set for a summit meeting with North Korea’s leader, Kim Jong-un, and that his administration was in constant contact about the fate of three Americans held in North Korea.

headline.main: Transcript of Trump’s Remarks on Giuliani and Stormy Daniels, and Korea
